🧪 Usage

Activate virtual environment:

onboarding_env\Scripts\activate   # Windows

Run basic check:

python onboard.py

Run with verbose output:

python onboard.py --verbose

Attempt auto-fix:

python onboard.py --fix

Run Pylint:

pylint onboard.py
📚 Concepts Demonstrated

Python virtual environments (venv)

CLI development with argparse

Environment validation using sys, importlib, pkg_resources

Disk monitoring with shutil.disk_usage

Performance measurement using time

Code quality enforcement using pylint and black

💡 Why This Project?

Modern software teams require consistent development environments.
This tool ensures reproducibility, prevents dependency conflicts, and improves onboarding efficiency.
